    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“从床上爬起来......”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >V 的噩梦就这样开始了：她是一位压力重重的母亲和妻子，被一个神秘的声音唤醒，并被拖进了一个被诅咒的电子游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在，她必须打败任何与她擦肩而过的倒霉蛋，逃离这个充满奇怪生物的疯狂低聚世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出路只有一个：打倒一切。用煎锅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/50e23d7e75ddc5180026e161082a8fa1.poster.avif?t=1756836007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/50e23d7e75ddc5180026e161082a8fa1.webm?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/50e23d7e75ddc5180026e161082a8fa1.mp4?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种类型。零怜悯。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >V's Rage》是一款手绘街机冒险游戏，灵感源自 80 和 90 年代的经典街机游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中会出现疯狂的战斗、荒诞的敌人以及随每个关卡而变化的游戏规则。每个关卡都会带给你全新的体验： 殴打、射击、枪战、侧滚轮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习、失败、发誓、重复。没有教程，没有指导。只有纯粹、经典的街机混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/1e9804e88acfedbceb02bef3d126aac4.poster.avif?t=1756836007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/1e9804e88acfedbceb02bef3d126aac4.webm?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/1e9804e88acfedbceb02bef3d126aac4.mp4?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>介于街机和 80 年代动漫之间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >V's Rage》秉承了《Final Fight》、《Altered Beast》和《Parodius》等老式投币游戏的精神。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它的视觉风格是手绘的 80 年代动漫能量的爆发，是对 Urusei Yatsura 和 Ranma 等标志性角色的怀旧致敬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/dfa7de125fcca5a4ad829b1f8de056ca.poster.avif?t=1756836007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/dfa7de125fcca5a4ad829b1f8de056ca.webm?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167530/extras/dfa7de125fcca5a4ad829b1f8de056ca.mp4?t=1756836007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
